dct_description_sm: This point shapefile identifies major cities in Kenya for 2000. Data from 1:50,000 and 250,000 topographic maps originally created by the Geological Survey of Kenya were digitized by the International Livestoack Research Institute and the Japan International Cooperation Agency.
This data was used in maps throughout Nature's Benefits in Kenya: An Atlas of Ecosystems and Human Well-Being.
